reviews: Great value for a pack of AAA! I only recently purchased so cannot comment on longevity.
Easy to install, super bright! Will update in the future regarding longevity.

Amazing product! Immediately made a difference! My son's room has the most sun and was the warmest in the house - even with thermal insulated blackout curtains! But this makes it the coolest upstairs room now!

My son loves it!

I did not read the description before purchasing (woops!) But it was a pleasant surprise that the comforter is reversible! My son loves the soft plushy side for sleeping under, and the typical comfort on top. Great quality, especially for the price!

So far so good!
My son loves his. It's his first bigger-boy cup (no handles).
It's been thrown and dropped countless times, no issues yet!
Good price for 2 large cups as well.

Got it with Prime Shipping in 2 days! It was already on sale and had a $50, so the price really couldn't be beat! I had never purchased a mattress before. This is my first new one. I was a little worried "What if I hate it" or "Will it be uncomfortable?" But OMG. First night on it after years of a supremely lumpy, hard mattress was amazing. I almost called in sick to work just to pay in it some more. I love this mattress already and it's a fantastic value!
Great stroller but not fantastic in any snow or slush. Still fantastic for the price and storage! Super easy to use.
Nice quality and warm! However, it was more of a slouch style.

Love it! My car doesn't have vents in the back and my son was sweating buckets while I was driving in Antarctica. Only hiccup is the remote needs doesn't have a good range, so when driving I have to reach in the back quite a bit and point to the mirror to get it to go again. A little longer range as my car is a normal size car would make this perfect for all!

Had mice in my new apartment. Installed these. Landlord also had pest control comez so I'm not entirely sure if these helped or not.

I bought them in the beginning of May. No reduction in spiders and now we're having ant problems. I have all 4 plugged in. My apartment is only 1000sq ft. I shouldn't be having problems. Unfortunately they don't seem to work for me.
Great quality vinyl. Super easy to wipe down. Just bring outside for a shake, or vacuum thgle crumbs up. It's currently saving my carpet from my 10 month old!
Looks great. Came quick
Works great. Even came with a spare, brighter white light. Instructions made it super simple. Will purchase again
Love this. Now the bottom of my dish drying rack won't get all grimy and gross! Just dump the excess water, give it a good rinse sometimes, and it's always in new condition
Easy to use. Works great.
I love my Brita. It's a necessity for me since I will not drink tap water

Ordered this for my MIL and when we received it, we received two of the same wheels so you couldn't even assemble it. Then when I contacted Evenflo, the wheels AND the play pen were on a few months long back order. Luckily, Evenflo was kind enough to replace it with a different one. Great customer service, unfortunately this model we had a glitch with.

My son hated everything. Bought him automatic bouncers, different swings, everything. This and one other thing we're the only things he loved and still enjoys now! Especially the little mirror on top. He loooves talking to himself in it haha.
Comes in a handy travel carrying bag! Couldn't find a better deal.

Came as expected. Large in size with numerous pockets. Husband loves it because now he won't have to carry something that looks like a purse. Only thing I wish it had was a specific wipes pocket to remove wipes easier!

review_title: Great for play and learning time!
reviews: Great toy! Bought for a three year old as a birthday gift. He absolutely loves it!

I loved the book and was glued from start to finish. Ended up realizing hours later I had read it in one night. I only put 4 stars because I found the book to be VERY descriptive. Not a bad thing, just not my thing. Great book nonetheless.

The blender is wonderful and I got it at a good price. It is extremely unfortunate that when it got to my mother-in-law on her birthday, we learned that one of the attachments was chipped up. Additionally, around where it was chipped, the paint was coming up. So it is unusable until we either take all of the paint off or risk it coming off during use.

My nephew loves this! Its so much fun for him. Does NOT come with the balls, for those of you unsure. Its fairly large but all detachable so its great still. Received it within two days.
Note: I did struggle with trying to get it all back inside the carrying bag. However, I always struggle with things lile that.
So far so great! Received it in 2 days. Holds a charge better than the original battery.

I've had this tablet case and keyboard since early February. It's so easy to use and perfect. I was sceptical when ordering but this case and keyboard combo for the Yoga Tab 10 were the best bang for your buck and great quality.
